One of the times I started and one of the employees was junior

01:03:05.220 --> 01:03:07.180
and he had just deleted it by accident.

01:03:08.010 --> 01:03:12.440
And I managed to go to each person's computer and recover a ton of the code

01:03:13.380 --> 01:03:15.240
and put a lot of it back together.

01:03:16.120 --> 01:03:21.060
Another time someone just deleted it and they, I feel were malicious.

01:03:21.980 --> 01:03:27.840
And then another time, basically we didn't want to wait for shared services.

01:03:28.180 --> 01:03:34.460
So the Canadian government decided we would make a department that was the IT department for the whole government and they just wouldn't give us a server.

01:03:35.080 --> 01:03:39.960
So we just took a server from another room and repurposed and decided that was our code repo survey.

01:03:40.180 --> 01:03:41.520
And so I set up a whole network.

01:03:41.580 --> 01:03:43.660
I set up Active Directory and all this.

01:03:44.020 --> 01:03:45.420
