01:03:49.340 --> 01:03:51.220
you need to back it up every night.

01:03:51.300 --> 01:03:52.680
And he promised me he would.

01:03:53.240 --> 01:03:55.040
And then five months later, it crashed.

01:03:56.500 --> 01:03:58.140
And he's like, are you going to make it go again?

01:03:58.700 --> 01:04:02.080
And it was a raid server and it automatically deleted everything.

01:04:03.900 --> 01:04:04.060
Yeah.

01:04:04.500 --> 01:04:06.280
And so I was like, well, get your backup.

01:04:06.320 --> 01:04:06.800
Did its job.

01:04:06.920 --> 01:04:07.380
It replicated.

01:04:08.420 --> 01:04:10.960
He had not backed it up a single time in five months.

01:04:11.700 --> 01:04:16.100
And we lost 11 contractors work for like months, like five months.

01:04:16.680 --> 01:04:18.320
I was like, I am so angry.

01:04:18.430 --> 01:04:20.640
