01:04:20.670 --> 01:04:23.600
I was like, no, I'm so angry at you.

01:04:23.740 --> 01:04:24.340
You'll make it.

01:04:24.480 --> 01:04:25.340
He's like, but I don't know how.

01:04:25.420 --> 01:04:27.040
I'm like, I guess it's tough to be you.

01:04:27.800 --> 01:04:28.340
You're going to learn.

01:04:29.420 --> 01:04:30.340
You're going to learn the hard way.

